<paragraph id="IFRS17_57" base="F55666391"><paranum>57</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 17"/><data name="paranum" value="57"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS17_P0230">If at any time during the <xref base="F55666921" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0520">coverage period<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0060"/></ph></xref>, facts and circumstances indicate that a <xref base="F55666942" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0526">group of insurance contracts<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0159"/></ph></xref> is onerous , an entity shall calculate the difference between: </p><ol id="IFRS17_L0043" base="F55666393" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p id="IFRS17_P0231" base="F55666394">the carrying amount of the <xref base="F55667010" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0551">liability for remaining coverage<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0228"/></ph></xref> determined applying <xref id="IFRS17_X0282" base="F59119855" href="IFRS17_55.dita#IFRS17_55">paragraph 55</xref>; and</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p id="IFRS17_P0232" base="F55666396">the <xref base="F55666938" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0525">fulfilment cash flows<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0143"/></ph></xref> that relate to remaining coverage of the group, applying <xref id="IFRS17_X0283" base="F59119856" href="IFRS17_g33-35.dita#IFRS17_g33-35/IFRS17_g33-35_TI">paragraphs 33&#x2013;37</xref> and <xref id="IFRS17_X0284" base="F59119858" href="IFRS17_gB36-B119.dita#IFRS17_gB36-B119/IFRS17_gB36-B119_TI">B36&#x2013;B92</xref>. However, if, in applying <xref id="IFRS17_X0285" base="F59119857" href="IFRS17_59.dita#IFRS17_59">paragraph 59(b)</xref>, the entity does not adjust the <xref base="F55667006" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0550">liability for incurred claims<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0227"/></ph></xref> for the time value of money and the effect of <xref base="F55666934" href="IFRS17_APPA.dita#IFRS17_APPA/IFRS17_P0524">financial risk<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0129"/></ph></xref>, it shall not include in the fulfilment cash flows any such adjustment.</p></li></ol></body></paragraph>